{"tid":1872206,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WHO抗疫新招 : 請微博、百度為疫情闢謠","createTime":"2020-02-10T03:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T08:29:09.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ea1b32d29b03c79db7c88ae794b10aa9115cffa8","tid":1872206,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T03:17:01.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情嚴峻，世界衛生組織（WHO）的秘書長譚德塞昨（9）日表示，WHO制定了一項新措施，以遏制2019新型冠狀病毒假消息的傳播。該計畫將會商請谷歌、臉書、推特、騰訊、百度、抖音、微博和Pinterest幫忙澄清錯誤的訊息(闢謠)，然而譚德塞所提到的8個社群平臺竟然有4個都是大陸的，網友見狀不禁直呼「這是要掩蓋事實吧？」、「請鬼拿藥單？」。<br />\n<br />\n據菲律賓最大的英文報《馬尼拉公報》（Manila Bulletin）的報導，譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）在媒體簡報會上強調，瞭解新型冠狀病毒是非常重要的事情，民眾必須獲得準確的訊息來保護自己和他人。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞還說，在病毒傳播的狀況之下，若假消息也一起傳播將會使得醫護人員更加艱難，因為這會令決策者分心去處理，並在公眾間散播恐懼、引起混亂。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞表示，WHO如今不僅僅是和病毒作戰，同時也在和陰謀論者、搗亂者作戰，這些人會傳播錯誤訊息並且破壞對疫情的防控。他聲稱，WHO的訊息傳播管理團隊正追蹤這些假消息的來源。<br />\n<br />\n另外，譚德塞也透露WHO將商請不同的搜尋引擎跟社群平臺來協助過濾假消息，並且從美國疾病管制與預防中心（CDC）、WHO那裡刊登準確的訊息。而這些平臺包括騰訊、百度、抖音、微博、谷歌、臉書、推特、Pinterest，當中可以看到騰訊、百度、抖音、微博均為大陸企業。<br />\n<br />\n同時，WHO還會向Youtube和Instagram上的網紅尋求幫助，希望他們能夠對粉絲傳播真實的消息。譚德塞說，為了消除這些大量的假消息，WHO本質上正建立一個傳達事實的紐帶。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2020/02/10/922589.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2020%2F02%2F10%2F922589.html&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVWLTbr5529Gqcy%2B2MeRGono%3D&h=0d359f92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2020/02/10/922589.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800xauto-er/s3/media/image/2020/01/28/20200128-074103_U7213_M588037_3076.jpg?itok=aGDi5vaE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800xauto-er%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2020%2F01%2F28%2F20200128-074103_U7213_M588037_3076.jpg%3Fitok%3DaGDi5vaE&h=1b207d95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(AP)"},{"pid":"9870520cd500994bf8bd86846804ecb3972314c2","tid":1872206,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T03:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c39b79269120098cbf29832a7fac678b47568a","tid":1872206,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T03:25:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"647c20f10e706618ddaa9fcc2f1b735c2a22a6f2","tid":1872206,"uid":260271,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T03:26:56.000Z","msg":"世界衛生組織 (真理部)"},{"pid":"deecc99496d588ae55716379db0678de107508d0","tid":1872206,"uid":18167,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T03:27:02.000Z","msg":"對中國黎講, 乜野都係政治事件, 但中國最鐘意話人將xxx政治化 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國際組織俾呢個極權組織一控制就會變成宣傳部"},{"pid":"4d55923c6c5d0a94b9578a3bddd76b024de12310","tid":1872206,"uid":315761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T03:29:16.000Z","msg":"黑鬼含到雪雪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有世界組織應該ban黑鬼參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"984c2fb20bd24256e600cb0e16b78de9cb5e4079","tid":1872206,"uid":58147,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T03:45:13.000Z","msg":"正，又助攻。<br />\n<br />\n最好闢到全中國14億人以為無事，<br />\n城市解封，<br />\n個個出街打邊爐食野味。"},{"pid":"9563535153c34d3e77b7439a41420ded8920bd57","tid":1872206,"uid":155137,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:00:59.000Z","msg":"WHO：不能有第二個李文亮"},{"pid":"37f4cac9fad5b53e07468b49fe4a7bf808e926bb","tid":1872206,"uid":9965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:22:28.000Z","msg":"讚成，等班支那狗乜撚都唔知，舞照跑馬照跳死快d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\